{"tid":2387869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大學生會候選內閣：12 閣員全部有被捕準備 遇打壓會守住底線","createTime":"2021-01-30T16:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T19:49:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"539c2fdff96ae749048534c67fe4b48ddff71df9","tid":2387869,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-12-%E9%96%A3%E5%93%A1%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99-%E9%81%87%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%88%E4%BD%8F%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2596%25A3-12-%25E9%2596%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AE%2588%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25B7%259A%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjEYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=68bd1630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2596%25A3-12-%25E9%2596%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599-%25E9%2581%2587%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AE%2588%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25B7%259A%2F&h=86a0d57b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3-12-%E9%96%A3%E5%93%A1%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%9C%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99-%E9%81%87%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%88%E4%BD%8F%E5%BA%95%E7%B7%9A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯「朔夜」候選副會長羅子維稱，早在 12 人「傾莊」時已曾討論被捕問題，「很感恩」全體上下閣員都有心理準備。他坦言在這個時間參選學生會，遭受校方打壓、記缺點，甚至休學或退學的後果，都在意料之中。<br />\n<br />\n談到內閣的政治立場，羅子維指內閣認為香港是一個「獨特的共同體」，在 2019 年後成為感情更濃厚的共同體，一起面對連串痛苦打壓。不過，內閣成員對未來仍然有美好期盼，希望在香港建立公義、民主的社會，希望藉著這些美好想像連結香港人，令港人更加團結。<br />\n<br />\n如「上莊」將促校方正視保安問題<br />\n<br />\n「朔夜」候選會長林睿晞說，中大學生會幹事會去年「斷莊」，相信很多人關心中大的人，都希望付出更多守護中大。內務方面，內閣指一旦成功當選，會促請校方正視保安組問題，對受打壓學生提供支援；至於外務則會堅持「香港共同體」及追求民主、自由、人權、法治的信念。<br />\n<br />\n林睿晞續指，內閣名字「朔夜」是寓意香港政治環境，如在漆黑夜空中伸手不見五指，但相信香港人會堅守，如天上繁星繼續為香港奮鬥，內閣的參選口號是「朔夜無光，夜聚繁星」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f20f6aa5d9322762f1c80f2a5d3736a360cd59","tid":2387869,"uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"學生會就嚟變非法組織"},{"pid":"f0d9e2116bcf3be8f610304771c4d806ffbca38f","tid":2387869,"uid":305767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />respect"},{"pid":"0ecedf7ec81ce61d2cc024958521dd56f85c9315","tid":2387869,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:10:33.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"0b797c044c9b96cab8b3e692373f5fc6602cd50f","tid":2387869,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:24:27.000Z","msg":"入中大讀書預左俾人拉"},{"pid":"9e0c6e77f63634a5d183eb3757d20e10063cfd96","tid":2387869,"uid":167931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:36:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3de2246ed29e11dc2f5af7468692e2a4c40524da","tid":2387869,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,